* graceCode --- a JavaScript add CSS compiler/minifier

This package implements a JavaScript and CSS compiler/minifier toolkit.  It is developed on [[http://nodejs.org/][NodeJS]].

The JS parser is implemented in [[../lib/parse-js.js][parse-js.js]].

The CSS minifier is implemented in [[https://github.com/fczuardi/yuicompressor/blob/master/ports/js/cssmin.js][cssmin.js]], which is a JS implementation of YUI Compressor.

* How to use
<pre>
$git clone git://github.com/starsun/graceCode.git
$cd graceCode
$node compile.js
</pre>